title: 2017 New York Pet Fashion Show images | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Every dog has its day! Furry fashionistas dress up for the 2017 New York Pet Fashion Show They say every dog has its day - and that seemed to be the case at the 2017 New York Pet Fashion Show The event, now in its fourteenth year, took place at the Hotel Pennsylvania on Thursday evening Dogs and cats - as well as their human friends - dressed up to the nines for the event Animals snapped at the fashion show sported both top hats and elaborate headdresses Many of the ensembles photographed featured sparkly elements on the furry fashionistas Published: 04:48 GMT, 10 February 2017 | Updated: 07:08 GMT, 10 February 2017 19 shares
